      <description>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html lang=&#34;zh-CN&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;head&gt;&#xA;&lt;meta charset=&#34;UTF-8&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;meta name=&#34;viewport&#34; content=&#34;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;title&gt;大模型API价格战：一场没有胜利者的军备竞赛&lt;/title&gt;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xA;* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }&#xA;body { font-family: &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #fff; color: #333; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 16px; max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px 80px; }&#xA;article { }&#xA;h1 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }&#xA;.lead { font-size: 17px; color: #444; background: #f5f5f8; border-left: 4px solid #5555aa; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 16px 0 32px; line-height: 1.8; }&#xA;h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #222; margin: 40px 0 16px; padding-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e8; }&#xA;h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin: 20px 0 10px; }&#xA;p { margin: 12px 0; }&#xA;ul, ol { margin: 12px 0 12px 20px; }&#xA;li { margin: 6px 0; }&#xA;blockquote { border-left: 3px solid #5555aa; padding: 10px 16px; margin: 16px 0; color: #555; font-style: italic; }&#xA;strong { color: #333; font-weight: 600; }&#xA;.red { color: #aa4444; }&#xA;.green { color: #2a8855; }&#xA;.thesis-card { background: #f5f5f8; border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px 28px; margin: 0 0 32px; }&#xA;.thesis-card .label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #5555aa; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 10px; }&#xA;.thesis-card p { font-size: 17px; color: #222; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0; }&#xA;.section-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin: 28px 0 8px; }&#xA;.grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin: 16px 0; }&#xA;.card { background: #f5f5f8; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; }&#xA;.card.green-card { background: #f0fff4; border: 1px solid #a0d0b0; }&#xA;.card.red-card { background: #fff5f5; border: 1px solid #cc9999; }&#xA;.card.blue-card { background: #f5f5ff; border: 1px solid #9999cc; }&#xA;.card h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #333; }&#xA;.card p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin: 0; }&#xA;.timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 20px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 2px solid #c0c0d5; }&#xA;.timeline-item { margin: 12px 0 12px 16px; position: relative; }&#xA;.timeline-item::before { content: &#39;&#39;; position: absolute; left: -25px; top: 6px; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #5555aa; }&#xA;.timeline-item .year { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #5555aa; }&#xA;.timeline-item .desc { font-size: 14px; color: #444; }&#xA;.warning-box { background: #fff5f5; border: 1.5px solid #cc9999; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }&#xA;.warning-box .title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #aa4444; margin-bottom: 8px; }&#xA;.warning-box p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin: 4px 0; }&#xA;.split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }&#xA;.persona-section { background: #f5f5f8; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 20px 0; }&#xA;.persona-section h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #333; margin: 0 0 12px; }&#xA;.persona-section ul { margin: 0 0 0 18px; font-size: 14px; }&#xA;.persona-section li { margin: 6px 0; }&#xA;.persona-section li::marker { color: #5555aa; }&#xA;.final-box { background: #111118; color: #fff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px 28px; margin: 32px 0 0; border: 1px solid #333355; }&#xA;.final-box .label { font-size: 11px; color: #9999cc; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 10px; }&#xA;.final-box p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: #ffffff; margin: 0; }&#xA;table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; }&#xA;th { background: #f5f5f8; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #c0c0d5; color: #333; }&#xA;td { padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8f0; color: #555; }&#xA;tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }&#xA;@media (max-width: 600px) { .grid-2, .split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } h1 { font-size: 22px; } }&#xA;&lt;/style&gt;&#xA;&lt;/head&gt;&#xA;&lt;body&gt;&#xA;&lt;article&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h1&gt;大模型API价格战：一场没有胜利者的军备竞赛&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;thesis-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;label&#34;&gt;核心结论&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p&gt;推理成本每12个月下降90%不是行业成熟的标志，而是AI基础设施化早期的血腥圈地——在这场战争中活下来的不会超过3家平台，其余玩家都将沦为别人的管道或废墟。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
